      <title>如何给使用虚拟机#2 之安装Windows系统</title>
      <link href="2020/08/29/post4/"/>
      <url>2020/08/29/post4/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>本文章面向小白，个位大佬请勿吐槽</strong><br>大家好我是保温杯，我又来<del>水文章</del>更新了</p><h2 id="下载windows镜像："><a href="#下载windows镜像：" class="headerlink" title="下载windows镜像："></a>下载windows镜像：</h2><ol><li><p>访问<a href="https://next.itellyou.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MSDN</a>网站（一个系统原版镜像下载网站）</p></li><li><p>登录MSDN，可以使用QQ快速登录哦·~</p></li><li><p>从windows10,windows8,windows7里选择一个系统，安装过程基本一样。我选择Windows7<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fuckzuoye/fuckimages@latest/2020/08/29/bf653532dba0b23a797f36d3c50f646e.png" style="zoom:33%;" /></p></li><li><p>复制系统下载ED2K<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fuckzuoye/fuckimages@latest/2020/08/29/0142ab245b015436671c0ca5dde3c5f8.png"  /></p></li><li><p>粘贴到下载工具里（比如迅雷）<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fuckzuoye/fuckimages@latest/2020/08/29/992396b3a02b525bed3adbd9b98d79a1.png" style="zoom: 50%;" /></p></li><li><p>等待下载完毕</p></li></ol><h2 id="在虚拟机中安装系统："><a href="#在虚拟机中安装系统：" class="headerlink" title="在虚拟机中安装系统："></a>在虚拟机中安装系统：</h2><ol><li><p>点击【创建新虚拟机】<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fuckzuoye/fuckimages@latest/2020/08/29/af559101ab746fbb24e770bd4a0cbbac.png" style="zoom: 67%;" /></p></li><li><p>点击【安装程序光盘镜像文件】并点击【浏览】</p></li><li><p>选择刚刚下载的.iso文件并点击【打开】<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fuckzuoye/fuckimages@latest/2020/08/29/2b95f2ae4c14459eb856d1b92807835c.png" style="zoom: 67%;" /></p></li><li><p>点击【下一步】</p></li><li><p>简易安装的用户名可以随便填，但是尽量不用用默认的<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fuckzuoye/fuckimages@latest/2020/08/29/fb0ed3d630b8e7ab27e46fe39dc96530.png" alt=""></p></li><li><p>提示”未输入密钥，需要稍后手动激活“点击【是】并点击下一步<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fuckzuoye/fuckimages@latest/2020/08/29/4c21c7e94ad531f5ae74de7099a950c3.png" alt=""></p></li><li><p>输入虚拟机名称并点击【下一步】<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fuckzuoye/fuckimages@latest/2020/08/29/dc9335b57bb71b305c8d25bf481c9d61.png" alt=""></p></li><li><p>磁盘容量建议设置为30GB，设置完毕后点击【下一步】<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fuckzuoye/fuckimages@latest/2020/08/29/ae8ed4f76e7583f7f3e1272e5089b667.png" alt=""></p></li><li><p>点击【完成】<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fuckzuoye/fuckimages@latest/2020/08/29/4e81adbe773024f4d222282e8fe38227.png" alt=""></p></li><li><p>等待和一杯水的时间让vmware配置磁盘，期间不要点击【取消】哦~<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fuckzuoye/fuckimages@latest/2020/08/29/2d964cf26e2b5072d341ff828c1df949.png" alt=""></p></li><li><p>然后就一路【下一步】安装Windows就可以了哈~<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fuckzuoye/fuckimages@latest/2020/08/29/15ac13bb0983aeea801d0624f5dc7563.png" alt=""></p></li></ol><p><strong>OK，搞好咯~</strong></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
